# Real 2026 fixtures + live scores via football-data.org.
# Get a free key: https://www.football-data.org/client/register
#
# Build time: scripts/fetch-fixtures.mjs reads this to bake src/data/fixtures.json.
# Runtime: the Cloudflare Pages Functions in /functions read the SAME value from a
#   FOOTBALL_DATA_KEY secret you set in the Pages dashboard (never committed).
# The key NEVER ships to the client bundle.
FOOTBALL_DATA_KEY=
